{"1. Gently clean it


Wash your face with a mild cleanser and lukewarm water.

Don’t scrub it. Just gently wash and pat dry.": 7}

{"Before you text, ask yourself:



Is there actually a reason they’d be mad?

Or is my brain just filling in worst-case scenarios?": 6}

{"Find m

Find b

Write y = mx + b": 7}

{"“I know you’re trying to look out for me, but when you go through my phone it makes me feel like I’m not trusted.”

“I’d really like some privacy. Is there a way we can agree on rules that make you feel comfortable but also give me some space?”

“If you’re worried about something specific, can we talk about that instead of checking everything?”": 7}

{"“I know you’re trying to look out for me, but when you go through my phone it makes me feel like I’m not trusted.”

“I’d really like some privacy. Is there a way we can agree on rules that make you feel comfortable but also give me some space?”

“If you’re worried about something specific, can we talk about that instead of checking everything?”": 7}

{"If you’re feeling worried about them splitting up, it’s okay to gently ask something like:
“Hey, I heard you arguing last night and it made me feel worried. Are things okay?”


You deserve to feel safe and to understand what’s happening around you.": 7}

